* [[span style="color: hsl(0, 0%, 46%); font-size: .8rem" class="vui"]]HUMS@@ @@[[/span]][[span class="vactivity" style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: bold"]]{$hums}[[/span]]
~~~~
